                     <p>1. Fol. 1a - a title (written by the hand of Maḥmūd b. Sulaymān.)2. Owner's notice and seal فى ملك الفقير الله تعالى محمود خليفه باب كوكللومان ابن سليمان بن عبد الرحمن ابن مصطفى افندى عفى عنه3. Owner's notice. Fol. 001a. A recipe (written by the hand of Maḥmūd b. Sulaymān) of remedies against hemiplegia, spasms, head-ache and diseases caused by phlegm.4. Seal of Libraire al-Arab (47 rue Faǧǧāla, Cairo).5. Fols 20a, 31a, 34b, 36b, 37b, 40a corrections written in pencil by a recent hand.</p>
